# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:26
translate portuguese welchsleepover_4b3ebb69:

    # "In the morning, I wake up with the sun shining in through the large windows of Nora's bedroom."
    "De manhã, acordo com o sol a brilhar através das grandes janelas do quarto da Nora."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:27
translate portuguese welchsleepover_1bb89dc0:

    # "She's not in bed with me anymore, but I smell the scent of fresh coffee coming from downstairs."
    "Ela já não está na cama comigo, mas sinto o cheiro de café fresco a vir de baixo."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:31
translate portuguese welchcoffee_b61ee1d9:

    # sst "Oh, good morning. I was just about to come up and wake you."
    sst "Oh, bom dia. Estava mesmo prestes a subir para te acordar."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:32
translate portuguese welchcoffee_0d43b64c:

    # sst "I made coffee."
    sst "Fiz café."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:35
translate portuguese welchcoffee_23486537:

    # sst "See, I'm not just a man-hating feminist."
    sst "Vês, não sou apenas uma feminista que odeia homens."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:36
translate portuguese welchcoffee_6d96fe98:

    # sst "I can make coffee for a guy if he treats me right. And you treated me so good last night."
    sst "Consigo fazer café para um homem se ele me tratar bem. E trataste-me tão bem ontem à noite."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welchsleepover.rpy:39
translate portuguese welchcoffee_736796a9:

